title: @sexy wukong, Every time I queue for Dynamic Queue, I get this message
body:
http://i.imgur.com/rDLWG81.png?2

Please help, I have bananas

replies.body:
To be fair, EVERYONE actually gets this error message currently.  This is a result of us [disabling the creation of Club Tags](http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/help-support/ih5gWw8j-56-club-tag-creation-disabled-and-server-error-message-in-client).  It doesn't actually negatively affect anything, it's just really, really annoying.  

TLDR, don't panic and click ok!
Fix it then, it's extremely annoying.

> [{quoted}](name=DemonicSniper911,realm=NA,application-id=osqw6G4M,discussion-id=daG3bBYr,comment-id=00010000,timestamp=2016-05-11T03:10:27.595+0000)
>
> Fix it then, it's extremely annoying.

They're working on it.
> We are working on getting a hotfix out in the near future to get this to stop appearing, but don't have an ETA just yet. We'll let everyone know if anything changes!
Because they totally aren't doing anything and just mechanically laughing at those of us suffering through just a click of a button.

It also messes with my friends list a bit.  Does not put anyone in the Suggested Friends list when starting a game lobby.  When friends come online, does not put them at the top of the list, but rather keeps them where they are in alphabetical order.
